- **Three in-body responses** at lines 14, 15-inline, 17 of the current Gdoc, replacing JC's `RESPONSE: []` placeholders. Targeted, narrative, brief. Pull content from the old 4-bullet block, then DELETE the old 4-bullet block (lines 18-22) so the summary appears only once.
