16: Reviewer 3 has asked for a modification of some of the intro that won’t make this paper seem so “timestamped”. In addition, he/she has some questions about the theoretical positioning.  I think that the paper will be stronger if the authors address some of the “tension” the reviewer identifies with a study that provides more clarity, but I won’t make it a requirement. On the other hand, they should provide a more nuanced discussion of the issues the reviewer describes.
